1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,858
Welcome to Meeting Your Self.

2
00:00:01,858 --> 00:00:09,871
This practice is an invitation to connect
with the core of you that can bring calm,

3
00:00:09,871 --> 00:00:16,419
curiosity, compassion, clarity, courage,
confidence, creativity, and

4
00:00:16,419 --> 00:00:17,787
connectedness.

5
00:00:17,787 --> 00:00:24,558
Beneath the busy thoughts, the worries,
the roles you play, and the emotions that

6
00:00:24,558 --> 00:00:31,074
come and go, there may be a steadier
presence within you. In IFS, we call this

7
00:00:31,074 --> 00:00:32,090
Self-energy.

8
00:00:32,090 --> 00:00:35,155
You do not have to make Self-energy
happen.

9
00:00:35,155 --> 00:00:41,722
You are simply creating space to notice
what is already available, even if it is

10
00:00:41,722 --> 00:00:43,468
only a small glimmer.

11
00:00:43,468 --> 00:00:46,394
Begin by finding a comfortable position.

12
00:00:46,394 --> 00:00:55,218
You may close your eyes, soften your
gaze, or look gently at one steady point.

13
00:00:55,218 --> 00:00:57,354
Let your hands rest.

14
00:00:57,354 --> 00:01:00,465
Let your shoulders soften.

15
00:01:00,465 --> 00:01:02,601
Let your breath be natural.

16
00:01:11,601 --> 00:01:11,601
<break time="3s" />

17
00:01:11,601 --> 00:01:13,737
Take a slow breath in.

18
00:01:22,737 --> 00:01:22,737
<break time="3s" />

19
00:01:22,737 --> 00:01:24,177
And let it out.

20
00:01:24,177 --> 00:01:26,313
Again, breathing in.

21
00:01:35,313 --> 00:01:35,313
<break time="3s" />

22
00:01:35,313 --> 00:01:37,171
And breathing out.

23
00:01:37,171 --> 00:01:39,772
Now begin to notice your body.

24
00:01:51,772 --> 00:01:51,772
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

25
00:01:51,772 --> 00:01:53,119
Notice your feet.

26
00:01:53,119 --> 00:01:54,094
Your legs.

27
00:01:54,094 --> 00:01:54,791
Your hips.

28
00:01:54,791 --> 00:01:55,580
Your back.

29
00:01:55,580 --> 00:01:56,834
Your chest.

30
00:01:56,834 --> 00:01:58,088
Your shoulders.

31
00:01:58,088 --> 00:01:59,574
Your arms.

32
00:01:59,574 --> 00:02:00,967
Your hands.

33
00:02:00,967 --> 00:02:02,174
Your neck.

34
00:02:02,174 --> 00:02:03,196
Your face.

35
00:02:03,196 --> 00:02:05,982
You do not have to relax everything.

36
00:02:05,982 --> 00:02:07,700
Just notice.

37
00:02:07,700 --> 00:02:10,022
Now bring your attention inside.

38
00:02:10,022 --> 00:02:11,555
Ask gently:

39
00:02:23,555 --> 00:02:23,555
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

40
00:02:23,555 --> 00:02:26,434
What parts of me are present right now?

41
00:02:38,434 --> 00:02:38,434
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

42
00:02:38,434 --> 00:02:40,710
You might notice a busy part.

43
00:02:40,710 --> 00:02:43,032
A tired part.

44
00:02:43,032 --> 00:02:44,425
A worried part.

45
00:02:44,425 --> 00:02:47,397
A part that wants to do this correctly.

46
00:02:47,397 --> 00:02:50,601
A part that does not want to do this at
all.

47
00:02:50,601 --> 00:02:52,784
A part that feels curious.

48
00:02:52,784 --> 00:02:55,152
A part that feels guarded.

49
00:02:55,152 --> 00:02:59,750
All parts are welcome to be noticed.

50
00:02:59,750 --> 00:03:00,632
Now ask:

51
00:03:12,632 --> 00:03:12,632
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

52
00:03:12,632 --> 00:03:16,301
How do I feel toward these parts?

53
00:03:28,301 --> 00:03:28,301
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

54
00:03:28,301 --> 00:03:33,874
If you feel open, kind, or curious,
notice that.

55
00:03:33,874 --> 00:03:43,089
If you feel frustrated, impatient,
afraid, blank, or judgmental, notice that

56
00:03:43,089 --> 00:03:43,580
too.

57
00:03:43,580 --> 00:03:47,156
That may mean another part is blended.

58
00:03:47,156 --> 00:03:48,317
Nothing is wrong.

59
00:03:48,317 --> 00:03:55,840
If there is a part judging or managing
the experience, gently acknowledge it.

60
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:57,465
You might say inside:

61
00:04:06,465 --> 00:04:06,465
<break time="3s" />

62
00:04:06,465 --> 00:04:09,019
I see you trying to help.

63
00:04:09,019 --> 00:04:11,991
You don’t have to go away.

64
00:04:11,991 --> 00:04:16,263
Would you be willing to give me just a
little space so I can listen?

65
00:04:28,263 --> 00:04:28,263
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

66
00:04:28,263 --> 00:04:29,610
Notice what happens.

67
00:04:47,610 --> 00:04:47,610
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s"
/><break time="3s" />

68
00:04:47,610 --> 00:04:50,861
Even a tiny bit of space matters.

69
00:04:50,861 --> 00:04:54,437
Now imagine your inner system like a
room.

70
00:05:06,437 --> 00:05:06,437
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

71
00:05:06,437 --> 00:05:12,433
Or, if it feels more natural, imagine
your Self as a wide sky. Thoughts may be

72
00:05:12,433 --> 00:05:18,428
clouds passing through. Emotions may be
weather moving across the horizon. The

73
00:05:18,428 --> 00:05:24,735
sky does not have to push anything away.
It simply has space to hold what is here.

74
00:05:33,735 --> 00:05:33,735
<break time="3s" />

75
00:05:33,735 --> 00:05:36,754
Parts may be standing close.

76
00:05:36,754 --> 00:05:38,472
Some may be far away.

77
00:05:38,472 --> 00:05:39,819
Some may be hidden.

78
00:05:39,819 --> 00:05:41,259
Some may be loud.

79
00:05:41,259 --> 00:05:42,838
Some may be quiet.

80
00:05:42,838 --> 00:05:49,061
And somewhere in this room, there is also
the possibility of Self-energy.

81
00:05:49,061 --> 00:05:51,197
Not as a perfect state.

82
00:05:51,197 --> 00:05:54,076
Not as something you have to perform.

83
00:05:54,076 --> 00:05:57,141
Just as a steady presence.

84
00:05:57,141 --> 00:05:58,766
Begin with calm.

85
00:05:58,766 --> 00:06:03,085
Notice whether there is even one percent
more calm available.

86
00:06:03,085 --> 00:06:05,221
Maybe in your breath.

87
00:06:05,221 --> 00:06:06,893
Maybe in your hands.

88
00:06:06,893 --> 00:06:08,658
Maybe in the space around you.

89
00:06:08,658 --> 00:06:10,237
Now curiosity.

90
00:06:10,237 --> 00:06:17,286
Can you be just a little curious about
what is happening inside, without needing

91
00:06:17,286 --> 00:06:18,178
to fix it?

92
00:06:30,178 --> 00:06:30,178
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

93
00:06:30,178 --> 00:06:31,803
Now compassion.

94
00:06:31,803 --> 00:06:36,168
Is there any part of you that could
receive a little kindness?

95
00:06:48,168 --> 00:06:48,168
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

96
00:06:48,168 --> 00:06:55,227
Even if compassion feels far away, maybe
you can notice the wish for compassion.

97
00:06:55,227 --> 00:06:56,388
Now clarity.

98
00:06:56,388 --> 00:07:04,300
Is there anything you can see a little
more clearly about your inner world right

99
00:07:04,300 --> 00:07:04,701
now?

100
00:07:16,701 --> 00:07:16,701
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

101
00:07:16,701 --> 00:07:18,234
Now courage.

102
00:07:18,234 --> 00:07:22,878
Is there a small brave step in simply
being present with yourself?

103
00:07:34,878 --> 00:07:34,878
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

104
00:07:34,878 --> 00:07:36,782
Now confidence.

105
00:07:36,782 --> 00:07:40,126
Not forced confidence.

106
00:07:40,126 --> 00:07:48,346
Just the possibility that you can be with
what is here, one breath at a time.

107
00:07:48,346 --> 00:07:49,739
Now creativity.

108
00:07:49,739 --> 00:07:54,244
Maybe your system has more options than
it first seemed.

109
00:07:54,244 --> 00:07:57,773
Maybe something new can happen slowly.

110
00:07:57,773 --> 00:07:59,398
Now connectedness.

111
00:07:59,398 --> 00:08:05,149
Notice your connection to your body, to
the room, to this moment, and to the

112
00:08:05,149 --> 00:08:09,290
parts of you that are trying in their own
ways to help.

113
00:08:09,290 --> 00:08:10,915
Now silently ask:

114
00:08:10,915 --> 00:08:16,348
What quality of Self-energy feels most
available right now?

115
00:08:28,348 --> 00:08:28,348
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

116
00:08:28,348 --> 00:08:29,602
And ask:

117
00:08:29,602 --> 00:08:33,503
What part of me needs that quality most?

118
00:08:45,503 --> 00:08:45,503
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

119
00:08:45,503 --> 00:08:51,029
If a part comes forward, imagine offering
that quality gently.

120
00:09:03,029 --> 00:09:03,029
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

121
00:09:03,029 --> 00:09:04,608
Not pushing it.

122
00:09:04,608 --> 00:09:06,558
Not overwhelming it.

123
00:09:06,558 --> 00:09:08,508
Just letting it be near.

124
00:09:08,508 --> 00:09:10,133
You might say:

125
00:09:19,133 --> 00:09:19,133
<break time="3s" />

126
00:09:19,133 --> 00:09:20,480
I am here.

127
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:22,430
I want to understand.

128
00:09:22,430 --> 00:09:25,495
You do not have to carry this alone.

129
00:09:25,495 --> 00:09:27,492
Notice what happens inside.

130
00:09:45,492 --> 00:09:45,492
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s"
/><break time="3s" />

131
00:09:45,492 --> 00:09:47,628
Now take a slow breath.

132
00:09:56,628 --> 00:09:56,628
<break time="3s" />

133
00:09:56,628 --> 00:09:59,925
And let your attention widen.

134
00:09:59,925 --> 00:10:02,804
Feel the support underneath you.

135
00:10:14,804 --> 00:10:14,804
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

136
00:10:14,804 --> 00:10:16,894
Notice the room around you.

137
00:10:25,894 --> 00:10:25,894
<break time="3s" />

138
00:10:25,894 --> 00:10:27,891
Notice sounds.

139
00:10:27,891 --> 00:10:29,377
Notice light.

140
00:10:29,377 --> 00:10:31,653
Notice your body.

141
00:10:43,653 --> 00:10:43,653
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

142
00:10:43,653 --> 00:10:47,740
Before you finish, ask yourself:

143
00:10:47,740 --> 00:10:54,288
What is one Self-energy quality I want to
carry into the rest of my day?

144
00:11:06,288 --> 00:11:06,288
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

145
00:11:06,288 --> 00:11:09,307
When you are ready, gently return.

146
00:11:09,307 --> 00:11:14,613
And as you move back into your day,
remember: Self-energy does not have to

147
00:11:14,613 --> 00:11:19,992
arrive as a grand experience. Sometimes
it begins as one softer breath, one

148
00:11:19,992 --> 00:11:25,734
moment of curiosity, one kind word toward
a part. That is enough. You can return

149
00:11:25,734 --> 00:11:27,697
here, one breath at a time.

